title: Vista User Account Pictures - Tribute to Mass Collections
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------
 Vista User Account Pictures - Tribute to Mass Collections
-----------------------------------------------------------



Installation:
-------------
 1. Unrar
 2. Copy over to C:\ProgramData\Microsoft\User Account Pictures\Default Pictures *
 3. Make a shortcut to this folder and move it to the "Pictures" user folder

Enjoy :)



Note:*
------
 1. Vista currently shows only first 100 pix&#039; in alphabetical order,
     so you may choose to copy only those you like the most
 2. Vista accepts only BMPs to display in control panel applet



Procedure:
----------
 Scanned through vast number of files.
 Photoshop retouche.
 Scaled to 256sqpx or in case where poor resolution down to 128sqpx
 Converted to BMP.



Greetings:
----------
 To all the authors!
 To all the people who uploaded various collections.
 Croatian uploaders.
